997a.htm| title = Hit Parade Italia \u2013 Gli album pi\u00f9 venduti del 1997 |language=Italian | publisher = hitparadeitalia.it | accessdate = 10 October 2013}}</ref>\n|14\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Oricon|Japanese Oricon Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"Japanesechart1\">{{cite web| url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/music/release/d/51638/1/ \u30c7\u30f4\u30a3\u30c3\u30c9\u30fb\u30dc\u30a6\u30a4-\u30ea\u30ea\u30fc\u30b9-ORICON STYLE-\u30df\u30e5\u30fc\u30b8\u30c3\u30af| title= Highest position and charting weeks of ''Earthling'' by David Bowie| language=Japanese| work=oricon.co.jp| publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon Style]]| accessdate=10 October 2013}}</ref>\n|20\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[RIANZ|New Zealand Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"NZchart\">{{cite web|title=charts.nz David Bowie \u2013 ''Earthling''|publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand]]|url=https://charts.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=David+Bowie&titel=Eart+hl+i+ng&cat=a|format=ASP|accessdate=10 October 2013}}</ref>\n|15\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Norwegian Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"norcharts\">{{cite web|title=norwegiancharts.com David Bowie \u2013 ''Earthling''|url=http://norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=David+Bowie&titel=Eart+hl+i+ng&cat=a|format=ASP|accessdate=10 October 2013}}</ref>\n|13\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Spanish Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite book |last=Salaverri|first=Fernando|title=S\u00f3lo \u00e9xitos: a\u00f1o a a\u00f1o, 1959\u20132002|edition=1st |date=September 2005|publisher=Fundaci\u00f3n Autor-SGAE|location=Spain|isbn=978-84-8048-639-2}}</ref> \n|40\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Sverigetopplistan|Swedish Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"sechart\">{{cite web|title=swedishcharts.com David Bowie \u2013 ''Earthling''|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|url=http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=David+Bowie&titel=Eart+hl+i+ng&cat=a|format=ASP|accessdate=10 October 2013}}</ref>\n|5\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Swiss Music Charts|Swiss Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"chchart\">{{cite web|title= David Bowie \u2013 ''Earthling'' \